          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SURGT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Fission cross section of 238Pu was determined",
                "using the surrogate ratio method. The (n,f) cross",
                "section was deduced from inelastic alpha induced",
                "fission reaction on 239Pu(a,af) (which served as",
                "surrogate reaction) with 235U(a,af) and",
                "236U(a,af) used as references. Cross section ratios",
                "239Pu(a,af)/235U(a,af) and 239Pu(a,af)/236U(a,af)",
                "were determined experimentally. Experimental ratios",
                "were multiplied by compound nucleus formation cross",
                "section and reference 234U(n,f),235U(n,f) cross",
                "section. Reference cross sections were calculated",
                "using the statistical reactions code STAPRE. The",
                "formation cross sections were calculated using the",
                "optical-model potential Flap2.2."
              ]
            }
          ],
